STATE of Minnesota, Respondent,
v.
Tommy James EDWARDS, Appellant. A16-1482 Supreme Court of Minnesota. Dated: April 2, 2018

ORDER

Based upon all the files, records, and proceedings herein, and upon an evenly divided court,

IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the decision of the court of appeals filed on August 14, 2017, be, and the same is, affirmed without opinion.

BY THE COURT:

/s/ ______________________________
